      1102,
      2049
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n\\begin{align*}\n&= 100h + \\frac{5h^2}{2} + \\frac{h^3}{48} - \\pi h^2 \\left(4 - \\frac{h}{3}\\right) \\\\\n&= 100h + \\frac{5h^2}{2} + \\frac{h^3}{48} - 4\\pi h^2 + \\frac{\\pi h^3}{3}.\n\\end{align*}\n$$"
  },
